TITLE: "Security ramps up ahead of possible Trump arrest"
DESCRIPTION: Former President Donald Trump was not indicted Tuesday, as he had predicted would happen, but security around the Manhattan courthouse where he would likely turn himself in if he were to be arrested has been beefed up.
